{
  "enabled": false,
  "name": "add-file-header",
  "description": "Add file header with copyright, author, and date information",
  "when": {
    "type": "fileCreated",
    "patterns": [
      "{backend/**/*.py,frontend/**/*.{ts,tsx}}"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "A new file has been created at ${FILE}. Please use Desktop Commander MCP to add a file header comment at the top:\n\nFor Python files:\n```python\n\"\"\"\nFile: [filename]\nDescription: [Brief description based on filename]\nAuthor: Development Team\nCreated: [Current date]\nLast Modified: [Current date]\n\"\"\"\n```\n\nFor TypeScript files:\n```typescript\n/**\n * File: [filename]\n * Description: [Brief description based on filename]\n * Author: Development Team\n * Created: [Current date]\n * Last Modified: [Current date]\n */\n```\n\nUse mcp_desktop_commander_mcp_edit_block() to add the header at the beginning of the file. Keep any existing content below the header."
  },
  "blocking": false
}